[SN]TITLE[SN]
Restoring the image of India's cricket league

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
The world's biggest, richest cricket tournament - the Indian Premier League is well underway - and this year there are two new clubs to replace teams that were suspended for corruption.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
20 April 2016 Last updated at 02:53 BST
So have the organisers done enough to restore the IPL's image and make it profitable for the teams involved? Sameer Hashmi reports.
